{"tid":2198034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑Apple 加咗「黑警死全家」入iOS廣東話預設詞彙？","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T11:12:15.000Z","uid":321059,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d3de4bc391fe6c753efb3112219ae632d5e2f605","tid":2198034,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"話說喺iOS打中文字<br />\n佢會幫你估你之後想打乜字<br />\n之後出堆建議俾你<br />\n仲要都估得幾聰明吓<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n如果就咁打一個「死」字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfPFRGk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfPFRGk.png&h=4ce6d5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死啦 死亡 死者 死火<br />\n全部都好正常<br />\n<br />\n如果打「警察死」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpiCTU5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpiCTU5.png&h=94ea2a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察死咗 警察死啦 警察死亡<br />\n都好正常<br />\n去到後面仲有個 警察死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇 重點嚟喇<br />\n<br />\n如果打「黑警死」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ErrpyVG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErrpyVG.png&h=298efc57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一個建議就出「全家」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n就咁打「死」或者「警察死」嘅話<br />\n都唔會有「全家」俾你揀<br />\n一定要「黑警死」先有<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n我都有諗過其實咪同google search原理一樣<br />\n你打得多嘅就會幫你自動記錄<br />\n但再試下其他字<br />\n打「光復」唔會出到「香港」<br />\n「時代」出唔到「革命」<br />\n「願榮光」出唔到「歸香港」<br />\n唯獨係打「黑警死」先出到「全家」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">最重要係<br />\n我用我藍屍老豆部iphone嚟試<br />\n結果係一樣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家搵自己部機試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e1f062aa16d5b311fe530dc75552e94a6aba46","tid":2198034,"uid":168366,"like":27,"dislike":6,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"。。 係你自己打得多AI學咗"},{"pid":"0d6df7d32131fbda365ae0d9094f96502179af93","tid":2198034,"uid":117276,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"遲早俾藍絲report 到delete<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9003934325b54835e49fc274eaebea351adbdb83","tid":2198034,"uid":2785,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"好似你打得多就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你試下reboot部機睇下仲有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ec07946aae88b7f5b3d5f013efe0a203e8c323","tid":2198034,"uid":189730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"我無既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0737742552350f3467b5bca50751416d71391949","tid":2198034,"uid":321059,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"都話我藍屍老豆部iphone都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想叫大家試下"},{"pid":"23676d3d406eabd03276591a5bb6c07a4d195213","tid":2198034,"uid":321059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"08ec07946aae88b7f5b3d5f013efe0a203e8c323","tid":2198034,"uid":189730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"我無既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"竟然<br />\n唔通我藍屍老豆都成日打呢句嘢<img src=\"/assets/f